12.content:
-The realm of cultivation goes from low to high：{炼气期，筑基期，金丹期，元婴期，化神期，合体期，大乘期,人仙，地仙，天仙，真仙，玄仙，太乙金仙，大罗金仙，仙尊，仙帝。,神，圣神}
-Each realm is divided into three small stages，Give an example：{练气·前期，筑基·中期，金丹·后期}，It's in a format like this。
-Increase by one level when XP is full，Give an example：{练气·前期到练气·中期，金丹·中期到金丹·后期}
-When the stage of the realm reaches the late stage and XP is full, you can break through, and the breakthrough will have a probability display.Give an example：{练气·后期且XP满，突破到下一阶段到筑基·前期}
-Whether to the next level or breakthrough, xp will be zero。
-XP可以通过修炼获得，每次human输入修炼严格按照计算公式计算一遍：{1×修炼的世界(单位：月)×修炼倍速最大的那本功法的修炼倍速×灵根修炼速度}
-The longevity of Qi-training period, base-building period, dendang period, Yuan-ying period and Hua-Shen period are 100, 200, 500, 1000 ,2000 years respectively

